snippet.title: RimWorld - Ideology trailer
snippet.description:
Buy DRM-free with instant Steam access: https://rimworldgame.com/ideology/
Buy on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1392840/RimWorld__Ideology/

What do you believe? RimWorld - Ideology adds belief systems to the game. Play as piratical nudist cannibals, blind undergrounder mole people, charitable ranching cowboys, machine-obsessed transhumanists, and many more.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/ludeonstudios
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/RimWorld/
